  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Bard - Masterpieces</strong><br/><br/><p>These stories of wiliness and mystery inspire listeners to see through deceptions.</p><p>Prerequisite: Perform (comedy) 5 ranks or Perform (oratory) 5 ranks.</p><p>Cost: Feat or 2nd-level bard spell known.</p><p>Effect: These tales include the stories of The Marriage, The Queen Mother, and The Rakshasa, among others. While performing this masterpiece, you gain a +4 bonus on saving throws to disbelieve illusions. You can expend 1 round of bardic performance for each ally other than yourself whom you want to gain this bonus.</p><p>Use: 1 bardic performance round per round, +1 round per ally affected.</p><p>Action: 1 full round.</p>",
